{"tid":2297970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粵普之爭 = 英法之爭","createTime":"2020-11-23T16:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T16:47:51.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed07b00a93ba707ce08f04174f0a1794e25a86cd","tid":2297970,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=080db230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/</a> LungZenoOpen/status/1330890684652429315<br />\n<br />\n其實，英法之爭，香港人既能代入法語，亦能代入英語。代入法語，法國人遇到外國遊客都說法語，不說英語。代入英語，前現代時期，英國統治階層是法國人，說法語，幾刺激英國人的盎格魯撒克遜主義發展。"}]}